Instrument Number: 20220404000974 Document:L Rec: $206.50 Page-3 of 4
Record Date:4/4/2022 2:57 PM King County, WA
STATE OF OHIO
-
COUNTY OF CUYAHOGA
Colleen Kirk, Attorney-in-Fact for HERC RENTALS INC. above named; being swom, says: I have read
or heard the foregoing claim, read and know the contents thereof, and believe the same to be true and correct and
that the claim of lien is not frivolous and is made with reasonable cause, and is not clearly excessive under penalty
of perjury.
By:
Colleen Kirk
Colleen Kirk, Attorney-in-Fact
HERC RENTALS INC. under POA dated 03/20/2020
On this 4 day of April
WILbefore me personally appeared Colleen Kirk to me
known to be the Attorney-in Fact for HERC' RENTALS INC. that executed the within and foregoing instrument, and
acknowledged said instrument to be the free and voluntary act and deed of said claimant, for the uses and purposes
therein mentioned, and on oath stated that she / he was authorized to execute said instrument.
In witness whereof I have hereunto set my hand and Ifused by official seal the day and year first above
written.
Notary Public
My commission expires:
may 27, 2024
TARA SCHILLING
(Ref: N222517 3033891 :: LE GRANDE VILLA)
Unofficial Copy
NOTARIAL SEA
STATE OF OHIO
NOTARY PUBLIC
FOR THE
STATE OF OHIO
My Commission Expires
May 27, 2024
